44:09.947 --> 44:11.914
On how to cheat on your wife
and get away with it.

44:11.949 --> 44:14.049
<i>My god.
That's not how I read descent.</i>

44:14.084 --> 44:15.317
Did you read it in english?

44:15.352 --> 44:17.252
Because, believe us,
that book is.

44:17.288 --> 44:19.054
A training manual
for how to be an asshole.

44:19.089 --> 44:21.790
What I read was the account
of a courageous man.

44:21.825 --> 44:24.259
Who falls into a true love.

44:24.295 --> 44:27.229
With a woman who isn't his wife.

44:27.264 --> 44:30.299
